#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1958
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-white\">The Classic package is designed for couples who "
"want to capture every moment of their special day. From the preparations to "
"the party, <strong>I will be with you from 9am to 9pm,</strong> documenting "
"your love story with my camera. You will receive <strong>at least 250 high-"
"quality photos</strong> that will reflect your personality and emotions. The "
"Classic package is the perfect choice for those who want a comprehensive and "
"memorable photo report of their wedding day.</font>"
msgstr ""

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1958
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-white\">The Deluxe package is the ultimate option for "
"couples who want to immortalize their wedding day with the best quality and "
"service. From the early morning to the late night,<strong> I will be by your "
"side from 7am to 10pm</strong>, capturing every detail and emotion of your "
"big day. You will receive <strong>at least 450 stunning photos</strong> that "
"will showcase your beauty and happiness. The Deluxe package also includes a "
"<strong>physical album with at least 50 pages</strong> of your favorite "
"photos, and a <strong>gorgeous oiled frame of 60 x 80cm</strong> that will "
"make a great decoration for your home.</font>"
msgstr ""

